embeds.title: Idoly Pride
embeds.description:
Owned by <@641544720157245441>. Original Anime by Lerche.

Welcome to the world of idols! Idoly Pride revolves around the struggles and challenges to become a top idol. Each of the idols from Hoshimi Production have their own reasons and purposes to become number one. Join us in witnessing the experiences of these idols and figure out who becomes the top one in the end!
